{"date":"2016-12-23","platform":"WEB","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/bc/a5/204868_1G11u.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/bc/a5/204868_1G11u.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/bc/a5/204868_1G11u.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/bc/a5/204868_1G11u.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/bc/a5/204868_1G11u.jpg"},"summary":"红豆，被古人视为相思的信物。三百年前嘉定方泰小镇上，春雨粘人。年幼的王初桐冒着雨将一颗小小的红豆放进了六娘的掌心，最初的情丝伴随着王维《相思》的诗句缠绕在两个人的心间。两小无猜的心心相印，青梅竹马的天作姻缘，欢笑、暖心的时刻却难逃时间的风吹雨打，年幼时的总角之乐，也化为 青春的羞涩与不安。当那扇敞开的门永远关上时，是否也将两人之间的情丝拦腰斩断？ \r\n\r\n那一天，天上依旧飘着雨，但执手望眼的爱恋已经化为天各一方的相思，他手握着那支红豆簪子，心知再也无法插到她如云的鬓发里，泪水和着雨水淌进唇边，相思的滋味，是苦的.。","name":"相思","name_cn":"","tags":[{"name":"国产","count":222,"total_cont":0},{"name":"短片","count":184,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2016","count":104,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中国唱诗班","count":90,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":62,"total_cont":0},{"name":"WEB","count":53,"total_cont":0},{"name":"恋爱","count":48,"total_cont":0},{"name":"独立动画","count":43,"total_cont":0},{"name":"彭擎政","count":22,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中国","count":21,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画短片","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"璀璨星空","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"中国动画","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"唱诗班","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"国产动画","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"历史","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"国漫","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"OVA","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"短篇","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2010s","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2016年","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"其他","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧情","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"国产或合作动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2023年观看","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"国产连载动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"李夏恩","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"国画","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"中国唱诗班之相思"}]},{"key":"话数",